1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:40,910
[Her Fantastic Adventures]

3
00:01:42,330 --> 00:01:45,420
My heart is sealed in the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword.

4
00:01:45,420 --> 00:01:47,750
So every time the sword seeker touches me,

5
00:01:47,970 --> 00:01:49,140
the power in my body

6
00:01:49,650 --> 00:01:51,210
will resonate with it

7
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,820
and the lost emotions and desires

8
00:01:54,370 --> 00:01:56,570
will return to my body little by little.

9
00:01:57,009 --> 00:02:00,390
The Black Wood Human-shaped Sword belongs to the sword seeker.

10
00:02:00,390 --> 00:02:01,650
I must return it to her.

11
00:02:01,970 --> 00:02:03,370
Why did you

12
00:02:03,570 --> 00:02:04,930
suddenly tell me this today?

13
00:02:04,930 --> 00:02:07,090
I have a favor to ask of you.

14
00:02:07,170 --> 00:02:08,270
Please go ahead.

15
00:02:08,410 --> 00:02:10,889
If I can help, I'll do my best.

16
00:02:11,090 --> 00:02:14,980
If you promise that the Duan family and Xiling can form an alliance

17
00:02:15,090 --> 00:02:16,130
and work in unity,

18
00:02:17,090 --> 00:02:18,490
then I'll draw the sword.

19
00:02:18,530 --> 00:02:19,490
What do you mean?

20
00:02:19,770 --> 00:02:22,370
The mark of the Star of Rebellion on Qing.

21
00:02:22,810 --> 00:02:25,030
Four of its petals has already turned black.

22
00:02:25,030 --> 00:02:26,160
If we don't save her,

23
00:02:26,490 --> 00:02:27,490
she will die soon.

24
00:02:27,890 --> 00:02:28,930
If I save her,

25
00:02:29,690 --> 00:02:31,420
she'll be Duan family's enemy.

26
00:02:31,610 --> 00:02:33,610
Your brother will not let Xiling go.

27
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:35,410
You're unmatched in this world.

28
00:02:35,410 --> 00:02:37,560
With you around, my brother may not be able

29
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,960
to do anything to Xiling.

30
00:02:39,130 --> 00:02:40,010
My heart

31
00:02:40,810 --> 00:02:43,820
has been sealed in Black Wood Human-shaped Sword ages ago.

32
00:02:43,820 --> 00:02:46,850
When Qing pulls out the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword,

33
00:02:46,850 --> 00:02:47,810
my life

34
00:02:48,410 --> 00:02:49,690
will end.

35
00:02:51,530 --> 00:02:53,730
[Episode 23]

36
00:02:57,700 --> 00:02:58,329
Senior.

37
00:02:59,170 --> 00:03:00,770
I was willful when I was young

38
00:03:00,850 --> 00:03:03,350
and wanted to explore the Martial Arts World.

39
00:03:03,350 --> 00:03:06,060
So I didn't take any responsibility for Xiling.

40
00:03:06,380 --> 00:03:08,580
You've been working hard because of me.

41
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:09,650
All these years,

42
00:03:09,900 --> 00:03:11,500
thank you for your hard work.

43
00:03:12,450 --> 00:03:13,980
We are fellow brothers,

44
00:03:14,330 --> 00:03:15,790
no need to be so courteous.

45
00:03:15,810 --> 00:03:18,010
But since you're going down the mountain again.

46
00:03:18,010 --> 00:03:20,250
I don't know when you'll be back.

47
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:20,870
Senior,

48
00:03:21,690 --> 00:03:23,850
I'll leave Master to you.

49
00:03:25,420 --> 00:03:26,490
Don't worry.

50
00:03:27,329 --> 00:03:29,130
If you no longer want to stay outside,

51
00:03:29,130 --> 00:03:29,850
come back.

52
00:03:30,410 --> 00:03:32,210
We'll wait for you in Xiling.

53
00:03:32,340 --> 00:03:32,900
Okay.

54
00:03:34,250 --> 00:03:35,810
No, no.

55
00:03:38,210 --> 00:03:39,870
How can I be the Grand Steward?

56
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:41,290
You are the Deputy Steward

57
00:03:41,290 --> 00:03:43,220
while I'm the legitimate Steward.

58
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:46,579
These are the accounts of Xiling.

59
00:03:47,490 --> 00:03:48,800
I've calculated everything.

60
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,210
Senior Bao has left.

61
00:03:51,010 --> 00:03:51,870
Second Senior,

62
00:03:52,090 --> 00:03:53,170
you have to

63
00:03:53,370 --> 00:03:55,430
take charge of matters in Xiling now.

64
00:03:58,040 --> 00:04:02,330
[To my teacher Wang Tianshan]

65
00:04:03,650 --> 00:04:05,000
What does this mean?

66
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:08,010
Open it and take a look.

67
00:04:16,089 --> 00:04:17,690
I ground it with plaster.

68
00:04:18,170 --> 00:04:20,300
I even lacquered a blackboard for you.

69
00:04:20,450 --> 00:04:21,970
This way, you can write on the board

70
00:04:21,970 --> 00:04:23,290
in class from now on.

71
00:04:25,290 --> 00:04:26,620
You can't even remember

72
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,600
any of the medical classics

73
00:04:28,730 --> 00:04:31,060
and just mess around with stuff every day.

74
00:04:31,570 --> 00:04:32,450
Forget it.

75
00:04:32,890 --> 00:04:34,440
[To my teacher Wang Tianshan]

76
00:04:35,530 --> 00:04:38,460
You've already given it to me, you can't take it back.

77
00:04:48,170 --> 00:04:49,930
Have you decided?

78
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:51,020
Yes.

79
00:04:51,580 --> 00:04:53,220
I am old.

80
00:04:53,250 --> 00:04:55,409
My hair and beard turned white.

81
00:04:55,409 --> 00:04:56,740
You're an old immortal.

82
00:04:57,530 --> 00:04:59,260
Despite your white hair,

83
00:04:59,890 --> 00:05:01,210
you are still very young.

84
00:05:01,210 --> 00:05:04,850
It's not good to live too long.

85
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,360
All my life,

86
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:08,840
I've received and sent away many people.

87
00:05:09,090 --> 00:05:13,930
I raised you up one by one,

88
00:05:14,290 --> 00:05:19,650
and sent you away one by one.

89
00:05:20,450 --> 00:05:21,450
Master.

90
00:05:22,930 --> 00:05:24,190
If there is a next life,

91
00:05:24,850 --> 00:05:26,580
I would still be your disciple.

92
00:05:30,130 --> 00:05:30,890
Today,

93
00:05:32,730 --> 00:05:35,250
let me comb your hair again.

94
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:41,040
[Penglai Bathhouse]

95
00:05:44,610 --> 00:05:45,330
I'm sorry.

96
00:05:45,630 --> 00:05:47,570
I have to bring something memorable

97
00:05:47,570 --> 00:05:48,730
away with me.

98
00:05:50,130 --> 00:05:51,990
So unfortunately, you'll have to

99
00:05:52,230 --> 00:05:54,760
travel around the Martial Arts World with me.

100
00:05:57,450 --> 00:05:59,190
[Penglai Bathhouse]

101
00:05:58,650 --> 00:05:59,730
What are you doing?

102
00:06:01,650 --> 00:06:02,450
Master Ruan.

103
00:06:11,050 --> 00:06:12,180
Where are you going?

104
00:06:13,090 --> 00:06:14,490
Where can I go?

105
00:06:14,810 --> 00:06:17,890
I just stopped by to take a look.

106
00:06:18,730 --> 00:06:20,260
Taking a look with baggage?

107
00:06:22,220 --> 00:06:24,210
It's normal for girls to carry a bag when they go out.

108
00:06:24,210 --> 00:06:26,250
There are always many things we need to pack.

109
00:06:26,250 --> 00:06:27,570
This bag is nothing.

110
00:06:28,170 --> 00:06:30,700
I thought you were going to run away from home.

111
00:06:31,090 --> 00:06:32,340
No way.

112
00:06:32,530 --> 00:06:33,220
Fine.

113
00:06:33,530 --> 00:06:35,130
Since you're not running away from home,

114
00:06:35,130 --> 00:06:36,490
come with me.

115
00:06:38,090 --> 00:06:39,620
It's not convenient for me.

116
00:06:39,770 --> 00:06:41,030
I have something to do.

117
00:06:41,050 --> 00:06:43,140
Maybe another day.

118
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,500
Young Master Duan is here.

119
00:06:55,050 --> 00:06:55,710
Have a seat.

120
00:06:56,690 --> 00:06:57,930
Why are you also here?

121
00:06:58,890 --> 00:07:00,330
I invited him.

122
00:07:00,530 --> 00:07:03,060
He will enter the Jiuqing Secret Cave with us.

123
00:07:03,090 --> 00:07:04,050
Why?

124
00:07:08,610 --> 00:07:09,370
Master Ruan.

125
00:07:10,450 --> 00:07:11,210
Master Ruan.

126
00:07:11,970 --> 00:07:14,260
It's not that urgent.

127
00:07:14,650 --> 00:07:16,650
Why don't we discuss it

128
00:07:16,650 --> 00:07:17,730
and decide later.

129
00:07:17,730 --> 00:07:19,210
Master has already agreed

130
00:07:19,290 --> 00:07:21,010
to open the Jiuqing Secret Cave tomorrow.

131
00:07:21,010 --> 00:07:21,930
Tomorrow?

132
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:23,770
This is too urgent.

133
00:07:24,130 --> 00:07:25,260
I thought about it.

134
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:26,170
Actually,

135
00:07:26,250 --> 00:07:28,780
I can find another Spiritual Treasure first.

136
00:07:29,340 --> 00:07:30,100
Qing.

137
00:07:30,490 --> 00:07:31,930
So you already know everything.

138
00:07:31,930 --> 00:07:32,860
I know nothing.

139
00:07:33,170 --> 00:07:34,370
Do you think that

140
00:07:34,450 --> 00:07:35,800
once the sword is pulled out,

141
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,050
I will die?

142
00:07:37,570 --> 00:07:39,050
That's ridiculous.

143
00:07:39,290 --> 00:07:41,090
I just feel everything's too rushed.

144
00:07:41,090 --> 00:07:43,370
Then why did you assign your position

145
00:07:43,370 --> 00:07:45,010
to Fu Rong and Lu Huahua?

146
00:07:45,330 --> 00:07:47,260
Why did you steal the group picture

147
00:07:47,730 --> 00:07:48,930
at the bathhouse?

148
00:07:49,770 --> 00:07:50,610
Qing,

149
00:07:50,900 --> 00:07:53,159
were you planning to leave Xiling alone?

150
00:08:01,170 --> 00:08:02,630
Since we've made it clear,

151
00:08:02,930 --> 00:08:04,460
let me be straight with you.

152
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:06,450
I heard you telling the Great Master that

153
00:08:06,450 --> 00:08:07,890
if I draw the sword, you will die.

154
00:08:07,890 --> 00:08:08,970
So I will never

155
00:08:08,970 --> 00:08:10,700
and would rather die than draw the sword.

156
00:08:10,700 --> 00:08:11,700
I won't sacrifice your life

157
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:13,450
to preserve mine.

158
00:08:14,090 --> 00:08:14,820
Master Ruan,

159
00:08:15,610 --> 00:08:17,410
there's no room for discussion.

160
00:08:18,170 --> 00:08:18,850
Qiao.

161
00:08:19,330 --> 00:08:20,290
If it's you,

162
00:08:20,810 --> 00:08:23,140
maybe Predecessor Ruan won't need to die.

163
00:08:23,490 --> 00:08:24,210
Me?

164
00:08:25,310 --> 00:08:27,410
How can I do that?

165
00:08:27,850 --> 00:08:29,770
It's not impossible.

166
00:08:31,020 --> 00:08:32,730
You're not only the sword seeker,

167
00:08:32,730 --> 00:08:35,690
but also the Star of Rebellion who can gather the Four Treasures.

168
00:08:35,690 --> 00:08:36,850
So?

169
00:08:37,809 --> 00:08:40,860
The Duan family has been guarding against the Star of Rebellion for many years.

170
00:08:40,860 --> 00:08:42,289
We know very well that there are many

171
00:08:42,289 --> 00:08:44,570
unbelievable things regarding the Star of Rebellion.

172
00:08:44,570 --> 00:08:45,530
One of them

173
00:08:45,770 --> 00:08:48,370
is to turn fate around with the Four Treasures.

174
00:08:49,570 --> 00:08:50,880
For Predecessor Ruan,

175
00:08:51,250 --> 00:08:53,450
you may be the sword seeker who will cause his death.

176
00:08:53,450 --> 00:08:54,820
But for the Four Treasures,

177
00:08:54,820 --> 00:08:57,250
you are the Star of Rebellion that can use their powers.

178
00:08:57,250 --> 00:08:57,800
Can...

179
00:08:57,800 --> 00:09:00,010
Can you make it more straightforward?

180
00:09:00,410 --> 00:09:01,640
Predecessor Ruan's heart

181
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:04,290
was sealed in the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword.

182
00:09:04,290 --> 00:09:05,370
To keep him alive,

183
00:09:05,730 --> 00:09:07,210
we need to break the seal first.

184
00:09:07,210 --> 00:09:10,090
As the original owner of the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword,

185
00:09:10,090 --> 00:09:12,950
you can help Predecessor Ruan to get his heart back.

186
00:09:15,290 --> 00:09:17,130
The purpose is clear,

187
00:09:19,090 --> 00:09:21,780
but the process is vague.

188
00:09:22,050 --> 00:09:22,490
I...

189
00:09:24,250 --> 00:09:24,690
You...

190
00:09:25,170 --> 00:09:26,530
Are you lying to me?

191
00:09:26,530 --> 00:09:27,650
Of course not.

192
00:09:29,490 --> 00:09:31,020
Without enough certainty,

193
00:09:31,170 --> 00:09:33,890
Master won't allow us to open the Jiuqing Secret Cave.

194
00:09:33,890 --> 00:09:35,690
You must have guessed it before.

195
00:09:36,010 --> 00:09:38,090
The reason Master didn't allow you to draw the sword

196
00:09:38,090 --> 00:09:40,210
was because he didn't want me to die.

197
00:09:43,570 --> 00:09:44,290
Qing.

198
00:09:45,410 --> 00:09:46,420
You once said

199
00:09:46,810 --> 00:09:49,940
if we don't give it a shot, we won't stand a chance at all.

200
00:09:51,330 --> 00:09:52,490
I hope to give it a try

201
00:09:53,010 --> 00:09:54,340
with this opportunity.

202
00:09:57,810 --> 00:10:00,180
Can I really do it?

203
00:10:01,170 --> 00:10:02,630
I'll do my best to help you.

204
00:10:10,530 --> 00:10:13,850
So this is Jiuqing Secret Cave.

205
00:10:14,130 --> 00:10:15,850
There was a restriction set around

206
00:10:15,850 --> 00:10:18,130
the Jiuqing Secret Cave by the Grand Master.

207
00:10:18,130 --> 00:10:21,370
Only the Great Master of the Xiling Sect can open it.

208
00:10:45,660 --> 00:10:47,130
So it was under the lake.

209
00:10:47,890 --> 00:10:51,090
No wonder we couldn't find it after searching for so long.

210
00:11:01,410 --> 00:11:02,210
Great Master.

211
00:11:02,670 --> 00:11:03,510
Don't worry.

212
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:05,230
I will bring Master Ruan

213
00:11:05,230 --> 00:11:06,470
back safely.

214
00:11:12,570 --> 00:11:13,170
Slowly.

215
00:11:21,730 --> 00:11:22,290
This way.

216
00:11:45,170 --> 00:11:46,050
Let's go.

217
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:55,750
What's all this?

218
00:11:56,310 --> 00:11:57,680
So cool.

219
00:11:58,540 --> 00:12:00,010
It's the first time I've seen

220
00:12:00,010 --> 00:12:02,790
such a mythical scene after being in the ancient period for so long.

221
00:12:02,790 --> 00:12:04,950
It's exactly like a television drama.

222
00:12:05,230 --> 00:12:07,770
This is the Mythical Stone Formation invented by our Grand Master.

223
00:12:07,770 --> 00:12:10,310
These stone monuments were made from meteorites.

224
00:12:10,310 --> 00:12:11,390
It's very rigid.

225
00:12:11,850 --> 00:12:13,230
Grand Master is highly skilled.

226
00:12:13,230 --> 00:12:14,630
The carvings on the stone

227
00:12:14,990 --> 00:12:16,730
is the Flowing Water Sword technique.

228
00:12:16,730 --> 00:12:20,090
The founder of Xiling Sect deserves his reputation.

229
00:12:20,210 --> 00:12:22,150
I once entered the Jiuqing Secret Cave,

230
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:23,480
but Master took me away.

231
00:12:24,710 --> 00:12:28,110
The Mythical Stone Formation had no abnormal movement then.

232
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,060
But I know

233
00:12:30,140 --> 00:12:31,630
there must be something strange about it.

234
00:12:31,630 --> 00:12:33,630
We should be careful.

235
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:36,460
Qing.

236
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:40,300
I'll go first.

237
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:03,670
Be careful, Master Ruan.

238
00:13:15,630 --> 00:13:17,420
There's indeed a trap.

239
00:13:18,230 --> 00:13:19,590
How do we get across?

240
00:13:20,370 --> 00:13:21,900
Don't you know how to fly through the air?

241
00:13:21,900 --> 00:13:22,600
We can't.

242
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,770
There are no footholds in the air.

243
00:13:24,770 --> 00:13:26,730
And it's too far away.

244
00:13:27,140 --> 00:13:29,610
And we can't touch these mythical stones.

245
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:33,730
Looks like we must pass this test.

246
00:13:34,170 --> 00:13:37,000
Since Great Master Zhang took you through the Mythical Stone Formation,

247
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:39,060
it means there must be a way to pass it.

248
00:13:39,300 --> 00:13:41,910
We must find a solution.

249
00:13:44,270 --> 00:13:45,800
This place is underground.

250
00:13:46,650 --> 00:13:47,970
Why is there light?

251
00:13:51,170 --> 00:13:51,970
That's right.

252
00:13:52,930 --> 00:13:54,940
The Jiuqing Secret Cave is underground.

253
00:13:54,940 --> 00:13:57,340
Logically, there won't be any light spots.

254
00:13:57,650 --> 00:13:59,880
This might be a hint to pass the test.

255
00:14:00,650 --> 00:14:03,250
Maybe we can try stepping on these light spots.

256
00:14:04,220 --> 00:14:05,150
It's worth a try.

257
00:14:05,770 --> 00:14:06,830
Predecessor Ruan.

258
00:14:07,130 --> 00:14:09,250
I'll go first this time.

259
00:14:11,370 --> 00:14:12,370
Be careful.

260
00:14:39,610 --> 00:14:40,740
You guessed right.

261
00:14:41,530 --> 00:14:42,290
Qing.

262
00:14:42,650 --> 00:14:43,730
You go in the middle.

263
00:14:43,730 --> 00:14:45,650
Duan Yu and I will protect you.

264
00:15:13,780 --> 00:15:14,480
Be careful.

265
00:15:14,850 --> 00:15:15,780
Are you alright?

266
00:16:10,570 --> 00:16:11,350
Qiao.

267
00:16:11,620 --> 00:16:12,140
Come on.

268
00:16:22,190 --> 00:16:23,120
Don't be afraid.

269
00:16:23,350 --> 00:16:24,110
I'm here.

270
00:16:25,270 --> 00:16:25,890
Qiao.

271
00:16:26,190 --> 00:16:26,990
You can do it.

272
00:16:50,810 --> 00:16:51,690
Master Ruan,

273
00:17:15,380 --> 00:17:17,380
the Flowing Water Sword technique.

274
00:17:17,700 --> 00:17:20,430
Master Ruan, the Flowing Water Sword technique!

275
00:18:02,220 --> 00:18:02,820
Let's go.

276
00:18:12,150 --> 00:18:13,870
It was so dangerous just now.

277
00:18:14,100 --> 00:18:15,860
Thank you for reminding us.

278
00:18:16,300 --> 00:18:19,030
There are traps in the Mythical Stone Formation.

279
00:18:21,130 --> 00:18:21,730
This way.

280
00:18:25,550 --> 00:18:28,260
Grand Master must have set up this Formation

281
00:18:28,340 --> 00:18:29,620
to let the disciples

282
00:18:29,740 --> 00:18:32,270
to master the Flowing Water Sword technique.

283
00:18:32,790 --> 00:18:33,430
Slow down.

284
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:49,340
This...

285
00:18:52,370 --> 00:18:55,500
Isn't this the sword used for our Sword Roast Whole Lamb?

286
00:19:04,650 --> 00:19:05,450
Yes.

287
00:19:05,870 --> 00:19:07,140
It's Grand Master.

288
00:19:08,110 --> 00:19:09,990
He looks exactly like the portrait.

289
00:19:09,990 --> 00:19:11,200
Grand Master passed away

290
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:13,920
and became a Sword Spirit to protect the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword.

291
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,650
Grand Master is highly skilled.

292
00:19:15,650 --> 00:19:16,980
You are no match for him.

293
00:19:17,330 --> 00:19:18,530
I'll handle it later.

294
00:19:18,580 --> 00:19:20,050
Draw the sword as soon as possible.

295
00:19:20,050 --> 00:19:20,490
Okay.

296
00:19:20,890 --> 00:19:21,950
Predecessor Ruan.

297
00:19:22,070 --> 00:19:22,980
Be careful.

298
00:19:25,790 --> 00:19:26,650
Don't worry.

299
00:19:26,760 --> 00:19:28,730
My heart is in the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword.

300
00:19:28,730 --> 00:19:30,990
I'll not die by the hands of Grand Master.

301
00:19:31,010 --> 00:19:32,860
Master Ruan, wait for me.

302
00:19:33,230 --> 00:19:36,020
I'll return your heart to you soon.

303
00:19:46,080 --> 00:19:47,370
Grand Master,

304
00:19:47,840 --> 00:19:49,270
I, Ruan Siqiong,

305
00:19:49,460 --> 00:19:50,860
am here to draw the sword.

306
00:20:04,530 --> 00:20:05,610
Go draw the sword.

307
00:20:05,610 --> 00:20:07,300
Master Ruan, take care.

308
00:20:19,310 --> 00:20:20,460
Is everything okay?

309
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:21,550
We're running out of time.

310
00:20:21,550 --> 00:20:23,880
Predecessor Ruan can't hold him for long.

311
00:20:27,460 --> 00:20:28,810
What should I do?

312
00:20:29,140 --> 00:20:29,980
Duan Yu.

313
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:30,980
Put your hand

314
00:20:31,170 --> 00:20:32,810
on the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword.

315
00:20:32,810 --> 00:20:33,730
Close your eyes

316
00:20:34,030 --> 00:20:35,960
and feel its power.

317
00:20:49,690 --> 00:20:50,570
Duan Yu.

318
00:20:50,600 --> 00:20:52,090
What are you waiting for?

319
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:15,580
Master Ruan.

320
00:21:18,250 --> 00:21:19,630
Why is this happening?

321
00:21:20,510 --> 00:21:21,260
Master Ruan.

322
00:21:21,700 --> 00:21:23,050
Why did you lie to me?

323
00:21:25,870 --> 00:21:26,870
Qing.

324
00:21:28,310 --> 00:21:29,300
I'm sorry.

325
00:21:30,510 --> 00:21:32,050
Don't blame Duan Yu.

326
00:21:33,520 --> 00:21:35,530
I asked Duan Yu to do this.

327
00:21:36,810 --> 00:21:37,650
Master Ruan.

328
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:40,170
Don't die.

329
00:21:41,470 --> 00:21:42,710
I'm not going home.

330
00:21:42,730 --> 00:21:44,970
I don't want the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword anymore.

331
00:21:44,970 --> 00:21:46,530
I'll return the sword to you.

332
00:21:46,530 --> 00:21:47,920
I only want you.

333
00:21:52,750 --> 00:21:55,510
Take good care of her for me.

334
00:21:57,420 --> 00:22:01,610
I want her to live safely.

335
00:22:03,250 --> 00:22:04,330
Go home.

336
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:07,350
I'm not going home.

337
00:22:09,170 --> 00:22:10,890
Xiling is my home.

338
00:22:11,810 --> 00:22:12,630
Master Ruan,

339
00:22:12,930 --> 00:22:14,090
I beg you.

340
00:22:14,470 --> 00:22:15,500
I beg you.

341
00:22:15,520 --> 00:22:17,010
Please don't leave.

342
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:22,040
Don't cry.

343
00:22:23,610 --> 00:22:24,550
Qing.

344
00:22:27,070 --> 00:22:29,000
I hope you can be a

345
00:22:30,110 --> 00:22:31,230
confident

346
00:22:32,340 --> 00:22:33,780
and happy child.

347
00:22:34,970 --> 00:22:36,030
In the next life...

348
00:22:38,870 --> 00:22:40,010
In the next life,

349
00:22:41,370 --> 00:22:45,060
I still want to eat your food.

350
00:22:46,330 --> 00:22:47,860
Master Ruan.

351
00:22:49,210 --> 00:22:50,740
Don't go.

352
00:22:51,360 --> 00:22:53,120
Don't go!

353
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:05,010
Siqiong...

354
00:23:05,300 --> 00:23:06,890
How did he leave?

355
00:23:07,090 --> 00:23:10,770
Predecessor Ruan turned into dust.

356
00:23:11,090 --> 00:23:14,490
He didn't even leave behind his body.

357
00:23:18,490 --> 00:23:19,810
I'm incompetent.

358
00:23:20,570 --> 00:23:22,570
I failed to find a perfect solution.

359
00:23:26,250 --> 00:23:27,570
I don't blame you.

360
00:23:27,890 --> 00:23:29,130
Just let Siqiong

361
00:23:29,130 --> 00:23:30,970
end the ill-fated relationship

362
00:23:31,420 --> 00:23:35,270
between the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword and Xiling.

363
00:23:35,680 --> 00:23:38,830
No disciples will suffer anymore.

364
00:23:40,300 --> 00:23:41,620
Actually,

365
00:23:42,530 --> 00:23:44,580
there's a legend in Xiling.

366
00:23:44,820 --> 00:23:48,760
Back then, Grand Master stabbed his heart with a sword.

367
00:23:49,010 --> 00:23:51,410
After he died, he turned into a Sword Spirit

368
00:23:51,420 --> 00:23:57,290
to protect the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword in the Jiuqing Secret Cave.

369
00:23:58,120 --> 00:24:00,670
Give this sword to Qing.

370
00:24:01,210 --> 00:24:06,010
This is Siqiong's wish after all.

371
00:24:15,130 --> 00:24:16,390
[To Qing]

372
00:24:27,930 --> 00:24:28,570
Qing.

373
00:24:29,010 --> 00:24:30,690
When you read this letter,

374
00:24:30,970 --> 00:24:32,700
I should have left you already.

375
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:34,560
Do you remember what you told me?

376
00:24:34,890 --> 00:24:37,060
People die three times in their lives.

377
00:24:37,080 --> 00:24:39,110
There are three deaths in a life.

378
00:24:40,120 --> 00:24:43,230
The first time is when our heart stops.

379
00:24:43,610 --> 00:24:44,540
The second time

380
00:24:44,620 --> 00:24:46,560
is when everyone goes to his funeral

381
00:24:46,560 --> 00:24:47,890
and remembers his life.

382
00:24:48,500 --> 00:24:49,380
The third time

383
00:24:49,690 --> 00:24:51,510
is when everyone who remembers him

384
00:24:51,510 --> 00:24:52,390
forgets him.

385
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:54,070
This is when we are truly dead.

386
00:24:54,070 --> 00:24:56,300
So don't be sad.

387
00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:58,020
As long as you remember me,

388
00:24:58,130 --> 00:24:59,300
I'll always be here.

389
00:24:59,890 --> 00:25:00,570
Qing.

390
00:25:01,020 --> 00:25:01,870
Meeting you

391
00:25:02,410 --> 00:25:04,290
is the luckiest thing in my life.

392
00:25:05,010 --> 00:25:06,340
Maybe fate is unfair

393
00:25:06,780 --> 00:25:09,040
and won't let me accompany you to the end.

394
00:25:09,050 --> 00:25:09,930
But if the Heavens

395
00:25:09,930 --> 00:25:11,570
give me another chance,

396
00:25:12,210 --> 00:25:14,610
I think I will make the same choice.

397
00:25:15,490 --> 00:25:16,570
You may not know,

398
00:25:17,250 --> 00:25:18,250
your arrival

399
00:25:18,980 --> 00:25:21,130
made my monotonous life

400
00:25:21,450 --> 00:25:22,970
shine with light again.

401
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:25,450
You made me feel like living again.

402
00:25:26,290 --> 00:25:27,340
You once told me

403
00:25:27,970 --> 00:25:29,650
your home is in another world.

404
00:25:30,130 --> 00:25:31,010
Over there,

405
00:25:31,530 --> 00:25:33,170
I'm your team doctor.

406
00:25:33,620 --> 00:25:35,020
Duan Yu is your neighbour

407
00:25:35,380 --> 00:25:36,770
and Bai is your friend.

408
00:25:37,240 --> 00:25:39,290
Maybe even you didn’t realize it.

409
00:25:40,010 --> 00:25:41,270
When you speak of this,

410
00:25:41,770 --> 00:25:43,300
your eyes sparkle.

411
00:25:44,650 --> 00:25:46,850
It must be a happy world.

412
00:25:47,530 --> 00:25:48,730
You should go back.

413
00:25:49,210 --> 00:25:51,010
As the team doctor,

414
00:25:51,730 --> 00:25:55,240
I must be looking forward to seeing you again.

415
00:25:56,320 --> 00:25:57,540
Qi Chunjiao,

416
00:25:58,190 --> 00:26:01,320
how long are you going to hide in the school's infirmary?

417
00:26:05,120 --> 00:26:05,850
Chunjiao.

418
00:26:09,510 --> 00:26:10,210
Chunjiao.

419
00:26:14,050 --> 00:26:14,850
Dr. Ruan?

420
00:26:17,550 --> 00:26:18,690
You can't keep

421
00:26:18,690 --> 00:26:20,290
avoiding your mom like this.

422
00:26:21,450 --> 00:26:22,630
I haven't gotten any results

423
00:26:22,630 --> 00:26:24,220
in three consecutive competitions.

424
00:26:24,220 --> 00:26:25,050
Every time my mom comes home,

425
00:26:25,050 --> 00:26:27,460
she would cook Sword Roast Whole Lamb to celebrate for me.

426
00:26:27,460 --> 00:26:28,520
If I see her now,

427
00:26:28,550 --> 00:26:30,010
it's like throwing cold water on her.

428
00:26:30,010 --> 00:26:31,770
I know you're in a bad mood.

429
00:26:32,050 --> 00:26:33,640
But how long can you hide like this?

430
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:35,320
As long as I can.

431
00:26:36,150 --> 00:26:37,610
Please let me stay here.

432
00:26:39,890 --> 00:26:41,620
Dr. Ruan, are you there?

433
00:26:42,990 --> 00:26:43,970
Yes.

434
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:45,940
Dr. Ruan, I beg you.

435
00:26:46,170 --> 00:26:47,090
Just once.

436
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:48,960
Can I come in?

437
00:26:51,900 --> 00:26:52,630
Come in.

438
00:26:56,300 --> 00:26:57,060
Dr. Ruan.

439
00:26:57,080 --> 00:26:58,560
Have you seen Chunjiao?

440
00:26:59,050 --> 00:26:59,730
No.

441
00:27:00,990 --> 00:27:01,850
I'm sorry.

442
00:27:02,820 --> 00:27:03,700
Mrs. Qi,

443
00:27:05,980 --> 00:27:07,800
I have something to tell you.

444
00:27:08,490 --> 00:27:09,550
Please take a seat.

445
00:27:12,370 --> 00:27:13,860
Dr. Ruan, please go ahead.

446
00:27:17,230 --> 00:27:18,220
Qi Chunjiao

447
00:27:18,250 --> 00:27:20,850
didn't perform well in the competition today.

448
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:24,530
How badly did she perform?

449
00:27:24,530 --> 00:27:25,770
Did she get a ranking?

450
00:27:25,840 --> 00:27:27,340
She's not feeling well

451
00:27:27,620 --> 00:27:30,820
so she wasn't in a good condition during the competition.

452
00:27:33,930 --> 00:27:34,690
Mrs. Qi.

453
00:27:34,710 --> 00:27:35,460
Chunjiao.

454
00:27:35,720 --> 00:27:37,170
Why are you hiding here?

455
00:27:37,190 --> 00:27:39,190
Why didn't you tell me your results?

456
00:27:41,490 --> 00:27:42,090
Wait.

457
00:27:42,420 --> 00:27:45,280
Whether I tell you or not, the results are still bad.

458
00:27:47,910 --> 00:27:50,040
-She really pisses me off.
-Chunjiao.

459
00:27:50,090 --> 00:27:50,890
Qi Chunjiao.

460
00:27:51,810 --> 00:27:53,460
Don't misunderstand your mother.

461
00:27:53,460 --> 00:27:54,990
I didn't misunderstand her.

462
00:27:54,990 --> 00:27:56,390
Since my dad passed away,

463
00:27:56,550 --> 00:27:58,510
she has never cared about my feelings.

464
00:27:58,510 --> 00:28:00,710
She doesn't care if I'm sad or not.

465
00:28:00,780 --> 00:28:03,670
If I don't care about you, who else should I care for?

466
00:28:04,110 --> 00:28:05,240
Who cares about me?

467
00:28:05,270 --> 00:28:07,050
You only care about my competition result.

468
00:28:07,050 --> 00:28:08,060
Qi Chunjiao.

469
00:28:08,280 --> 00:28:09,880
You can't tell good from bad?

470
00:28:10,210 --> 00:28:11,870
Don't go home if you dare

471
00:28:12,010 --> 00:28:13,870
and keep hiding at the infirmary.

472
00:28:14,740 --> 00:28:15,690
Mrs. Qi.

473
00:28:15,900 --> 00:28:16,410
This...

474
00:28:18,490 --> 00:28:19,250
Chunjiao.

475
00:28:19,270 --> 00:28:20,940
How could you talk to your mother like that?

476
00:28:20,940 --> 00:28:22,770
Go and apologize to her later.

477
00:28:24,460 --> 00:28:25,290
Chunjiao.

478
00:28:25,840 --> 00:28:28,040
Your mother forgot the barbeque sword.

479
00:28:32,130 --> 00:28:33,510
The Black Wood Human-shaped Sword?

480
00:28:33,510 --> 00:28:34,440
Listen to me.

481
00:28:34,560 --> 00:28:36,660
Your mother is also in a difficult position.

482
00:28:36,660 --> 00:28:37,580
-Master Ruan.
-Sometimes

483
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:39,780
you should think from her perspective.

484
00:28:42,250 --> 00:28:43,180
Master Ruan.

485
00:28:43,200 --> 00:28:44,140
Don't just stand there.

486
00:28:44,140 --> 00:28:45,490
Go find your mom.

487
00:28:54,690 --> 00:29:00,860
♫In the bustling place, a brief look back♫

488
00:29:02,240 --> 00:29:07,920
♫You raised your head, and the fireworks flashed across the night sky♫

489
00:29:06,570 --> 00:29:07,620
Liar!

490
00:29:08,380 --> 00:29:09,820
You lied to me!

491
00:29:09,860 --> 00:29:11,590
♫The night breezes played music gently♫

492
00:29:10,210 --> 00:29:11,770
I don't want this sword.

493
00:29:11,660 --> 00:29:13,060
♫Even flying birds stopped♫

494
00:29:11,770 --> 00:29:13,610
Come back.

495
00:29:13,140 --> 00:29:17,020
♫To review your gentleness♫

496
00:29:15,240 --> 00:29:16,770
You lied to me.

497
00:29:17,080 --> 00:29:17,880
♫The biggest fear is that in my dream♫

498
00:29:17,910 --> 00:29:22,380
♫I can't see your smile♫

499
00:29:22,490 --> 00:29:26,260
♫Until the end♫

500
00:29:23,210 --> 00:29:27,050
[Grave of Beloved Disciple Guan Mu] [Grave of Beloved Disciple Man Tianxin]

501
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:28,590
♫Love doesn't need to be put together♫

502
00:29:28,650 --> 00:29:32,910
♫Feel it with your heart♫

503
00:29:33,640 --> 00:29:35,800
♫Whether it's autumn or winter, I've been missing you♫

504
00:29:36,170 --> 00:29:42,030
♫Even if my hair turns grey as time goes by♫

505
00:29:37,050 --> 00:29:38,010
Qiao.

506
00:29:42,110 --> 00:29:45,650
♫Meeting you is my only reason♫

507
00:29:45,690 --> 00:29:49,790
♫I persist in it for you in the crowd♫

508
00:29:49,890 --> 00:29:58,840
♫No matter how long the journey is, we'll stay by each other's side♫

509
00:29:55,530 --> 00:29:58,890
The Grand Master of Xiling died with a sword through his heart.

510
00:29:58,890 --> 00:30:00,350
And Predecessor Ruan's heart

511
00:30:00,350 --> 00:30:03,080
was sealed in the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword.

512
00:30:03,970 --> 00:30:04,830
Do you think...

513
00:30:05,120 --> 00:30:05,730
Yes.

514
00:30:06,370 --> 00:30:09,400
Master Ruan will definitely become a Sword Spirit.

515
00:30:11,100 --> 00:30:17,190
♫Lift your head, I'll kiss your forehead♫

516
00:30:13,410 --> 00:30:14,450
Master Ruan.

517
00:30:15,770 --> 00:30:16,970
You have to work hard.

518
00:30:18,410 --> 00:30:24,020
♫Holding hands, we pay no heed to the starry sky♫

519
00:30:18,650 --> 00:30:20,090
See you next time.

520
00:30:20,850 --> 00:30:22,580
It'll be my turn to protect you.

521
00:30:26,190 --> 00:30:26,970
Qiao.

522
00:30:26,250 --> 00:30:27,990
♫I forgot what to say♫

523
00:30:28,040 --> 00:30:29,410
♫The clock's hands forgot to move♫

524
00:30:28,240 --> 00:30:29,490
I haven't told you,

525
00:30:29,500 --> 00:30:33,460
♫Waiting for you to let me stay♫

526
00:30:30,810 --> 00:30:32,470
I've found the Meridian Gate.

527
00:30:33,510 --> 00:30:34,250
♫The biggest fear when I awake♫

528
00:30:33,730 --> 00:30:34,350
Where is it?

529
00:30:34,350 --> 00:30:38,440
♫I can't touch your face♫

530
00:30:34,770 --> 00:30:35,810
In the Fire Crane Tribe.

531
00:30:35,810 --> 00:30:36,940
I'll get it with you.

532
00:30:37,290 --> 00:30:38,020
Don't worry.

533
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:40,200
I won't let you get hurt again.

534
00:30:38,930 --> 00:30:42,570
♫After dawn♫

535
00:30:40,730 --> 00:30:42,650
I'll look for the Four Treasures with you.

536
00:30:42,650 --> 00:30:43,410
I'll go with you.

537
00:30:42,980 --> 00:30:45,010
♫Love doesn't need to be put together♫

538
00:30:44,720 --> 00:30:45,600
But the Four Treasures...

539
00:30:45,060 --> 00:30:49,310
♫Feel it with your heart♫

540
00:30:47,010 --> 00:30:48,270
I'll find them myself.

541
00:30:48,620 --> 00:30:49,450
Qiao.

542
00:30:49,530 --> 00:30:50,890
I don't want you to be like Master Ruan.

543
00:30:50,010 --> 00:30:52,140
♫Whether it's autumn or winter, I've been missing you♫

544
00:30:52,600 --> 00:30:58,470
♫Even if my hair turns grey as time goes by♫

545
00:30:53,070 --> 00:30:57,410
[Xiling Sect]

546
00:30:58,530 --> 00:31:02,190
♫Meeting you is my only reason♫

547
00:31:02,250 --> 00:31:06,250
♫I persist in it for you in the crowd♫

548
00:31:06,290 --> 00:31:15,190
♫No matter how long the journey is, we'll stay by each other's side♫

549
00:31:07,290 --> 00:31:08,050
Qiao.

550
00:31:08,690 --> 00:31:10,570
Why did you choose to leave without saying goodbye?

551
00:31:10,570 --> 00:31:11,830
I'm afraid of parting.

552
00:31:11,970 --> 00:31:13,700
