00:31:47,850 --> 00:31:50,340
If you say so, it must be true.

565
00:31:51,500 --> 00:31:53,870
I wonder if Duan Yu has found Gu Qingqiao.

566
00:31:54,560 --> 00:31:55,500
Young Master Shaoyi,

567
00:31:55,500 --> 00:31:57,510
do you miss him

568
00:31:57,540 --> 00:31:59,180
or Miss Gu?

569
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:01,920
When I didn't know Wu,

570
00:32:02,130 --> 00:32:04,730
I couldn't understand Duan Yu and Gu Qingqiao.

571
00:32:05,450 --> 00:32:07,090
But now I understand them.

572
00:32:07,300 --> 00:32:09,090
I feel sorry for them.

573
00:32:09,770 --> 00:32:11,290
I want them to come back

574
00:32:11,530 --> 00:32:12,820
but also don't.

575
00:32:13,450 --> 00:32:15,250
What's the use of feeling sorry for them?

576
00:32:15,250 --> 00:32:16,250
Anyway,

577
00:32:16,270 --> 00:32:18,530
His Lordship won't let them be together.

578
00:32:19,860 --> 00:32:20,740
You...

579
00:32:20,970 --> 00:32:21,810
Shut up.

580
00:32:25,770 --> 00:32:27,520
Xing Si, take a rest.

581
00:32:27,660 --> 00:32:28,620
Find a carriage.

582
00:32:28,730 --> 00:32:29,170
Okay.

583
00:32:33,650 --> 00:32:35,050
Qiao, here.

584
00:32:41,010 --> 00:32:41,850
How are you?

585
00:32:42,770 --> 00:32:43,470
I'm fine.

586
00:32:43,610 --> 00:32:44,920
You can take the carriage later.

587
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:45,840
It's okay.

588
00:32:46,470 --> 00:32:48,540
Our priority is to go to the Fire Crane Tribe first.

589
00:32:48,540 --> 00:32:50,090
Listen to me. Don't act tough.

590
00:32:50,090 --> 00:32:50,720
All right.

591
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:53,800
It's more important to find the Meridian Gate.

592
00:33:09,130 --> 00:33:11,210
Did Great Master say

593
00:33:11,210 --> 00:33:12,210
how to awaken

594
00:33:12,230 --> 00:33:14,370
the Sword Spirit of Black Wood Human-shaped Sword?

595
00:33:14,370 --> 00:33:15,370
I asked him before

596
00:33:16,120 --> 00:33:18,050
and I found that Great Master Zhang

597
00:33:18,050 --> 00:33:19,310
also doesn't know how.

598
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:32,880
Qiao, what are you doing?

599
00:33:34,130 --> 00:33:36,260
I once read in a novel

600
00:33:36,440 --> 00:33:38,970
that a Spiritual Treasure can be awakened with blood.

601
00:33:38,970 --> 00:33:40,170
I want to try.

602
00:33:40,970 --> 00:33:42,830
Why are you messing around again?

603
00:33:46,130 --> 00:33:46,980
I'm fine.

604
00:33:47,010 --> 00:33:48,330
It's just a scratch.

605
00:33:52,770 --> 00:33:53,490
You...

606
00:33:54,530 --> 00:33:55,730
still keep it?

607
00:33:58,300 --> 00:33:59,700
I always carry it with me.

608
00:34:02,960 --> 00:34:04,040
You told me

609
00:34:04,690 --> 00:34:06,620
putting the ring on the ring finger

610
00:34:07,250 --> 00:34:10,130
means that two people's hearts are connected.

611
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:25,139
That was a long time ago.

612
00:34:34,239 --> 00:34:36,840
I thought I made myself clear.

613
00:34:37,989 --> 00:34:40,370
Whether we can gather the Four Treasures or not,

614
00:34:40,370 --> 00:34:42,100
we will go on our separate ways.

615
00:34:43,510 --> 00:34:44,500
I know.

616
00:34:45,179 --> 00:34:46,330
We'll part ways

617
00:34:50,449 --> 00:34:52,310
and be distanced from each other.

618
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:58,560
We are like people from two worlds.

619
00:34:59,770 --> 00:35:00,970
The fish in the water

620
00:35:01,700 --> 00:35:03,050
and birds in the sky

621
00:35:03,730 --> 00:35:05,180
cannot be together.

622
00:35:09,890 --> 00:35:11,290
For us,

623
00:35:11,910 --> 00:35:15,540
the best way to say goodbye is to smile.

624
00:35:17,130 --> 00:35:19,430
I couldn't do that in Changqing.

625
00:35:20,930 --> 00:35:22,640
This time, I hope we can bid

626
00:35:23,610 --> 00:35:26,940
a nonchalant farewell when the gate of time and space opens.

627
00:35:28,690 --> 00:35:29,290
Okay.

628
00:35:30,290 --> 00:35:31,090
I promise you.

629
00:35:31,850 --> 00:35:33,020
When that day comes,

630
00:35:33,850 --> 00:35:36,460
I will send you off with a smile.

631
00:35:42,270 --> 00:35:43,110
Deal.

632
00:35:45,810 --> 00:35:46,730
Deal.

633
00:35:49,990 --> 00:35:52,030
I'm starving.

634
00:35:50,600 --> 00:35:51,700
[Posthouse]

635
00:35:52,130 --> 00:35:55,280
[Posthouse]

636
00:35:55,260 --> 00:35:56,050
Ruoyi.

637
00:35:56,250 --> 00:35:58,850
Why hasn't the person who's gone hunting come back yet?

638
00:35:58,850 --> 00:36:00,420
He's been gone for a while.

639
00:36:00,420 --> 00:36:01,530
He should be back soon.

640
00:36:01,530 --> 00:36:03,060
When he brings back the pheasant,

641
00:36:03,060 --> 00:36:04,090
I’ll roast it.

642
00:36:04,090 --> 00:36:06,490
I really miss Miss Gu’s barbecue.

643
00:36:06,520 --> 00:36:07,900
Do you think you are the only one who misses it?

644
00:36:07,900 --> 00:36:09,450
I want to eat it too.

645
00:36:15,610 --> 00:36:16,260
Uncle.

646
00:36:16,260 --> 00:36:16,820
My uncle.

647
00:36:16,820 --> 00:36:17,770
Young Master.

648
00:36:19,010 --> 00:36:19,690
Shaoyi.

649
00:36:19,950 --> 00:36:21,950
How did you know I would pass by here?

650
00:36:21,980 --> 00:36:23,540
I've been out for days.

651
00:36:23,610 --> 00:36:25,460
I've been staying at this posthouse every day

652
00:36:25,460 --> 00:36:26,990
to wait for you to come back.

653
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:30,520
You were in a hurry to meet Wu, weren't you?

654
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:33,260
Yes, I even prepared a gift for her.

655
00:36:33,490 --> 00:36:35,030
You didn't even attempt to hide it.

656
00:36:35,030 --> 00:36:36,310
It's true that I like her.

657
00:36:36,310 --> 00:36:37,580
What's there to hide?

658
00:36:37,380 --> 00:36:39,100
[Posthouse]

659
00:36:41,010 --> 00:36:41,850
Shaoyi.

660
00:36:42,850 --> 00:36:44,730
We were just thinking about your barbecue

661
00:36:44,730 --> 00:36:45,660
and you arrived.

662
00:36:46,030 --> 00:36:47,570
I'll cook for you later.

663
00:36:47,930 --> 00:36:48,630
Shaoyi,

664
00:36:49,010 --> 00:36:51,410
you said you saw the Four Treasures before.

665
00:36:51,470 --> 00:36:52,830
What do they look like?

666
00:36:54,010 --> 00:36:55,490
It's a necklace.

667
00:36:55,490 --> 00:36:57,060
And there's a portrait inside.

668
00:36:57,060 --> 00:36:59,110
It looks exactly like you.

669
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:01,400
It's like your soul was sealed

670
00:37:01,490 --> 00:37:02,490
in the necklace.

671
00:37:02,640 --> 00:37:03,220
Yes.

672
00:37:03,610 --> 00:37:04,570
Uncle said

673
00:37:04,590 --> 00:37:07,920
you look exactly like the Priestess of the Fire Crane Tribe.

674
00:37:08,250 --> 00:37:08,970
Do you know?

675
00:37:09,070 --> 00:37:10,580
My uncle went through a lot

676
00:37:10,620 --> 00:37:12,970
to get this necklace.

677
00:37:15,590 --> 00:37:16,670
It's a bit too much.

678
00:37:16,700 --> 00:37:18,140
A portrait.

679
00:37:19,740 --> 00:37:20,890
A portrait?

680
00:37:21,110 --> 00:37:23,460
Do you mean a photo?

681
00:37:24,210 --> 00:37:25,020
Photo?

682
00:37:25,390 --> 00:37:26,120
What is that?

683
00:37:27,130 --> 00:37:28,990
You place a camera

684
00:37:29,100 --> 00:37:31,360
in front of your face and press the button

685
00:37:31,370 --> 00:37:32,570
so you can record

686
00:37:32,570 --> 00:37:35,430
your facial expression, clothing and background.

687
00:37:37,170 --> 00:37:41,330
It's something that exists in our world.

688
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:57,850
Who is he?

689
00:38:01,610 --> 00:38:02,810
A guest from afar.

690
00:38:03,170 --> 00:38:03,690
You...

691
00:38:03,710 --> 00:38:06,080
Why did you come to the Fire Crane Tribe?

692
00:38:06,110 --> 00:38:07,710
I'm here to look for someone.

693
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:08,660
Who are you looking for?

694
00:38:08,660 --> 00:38:09,390
Duan Yu.

695
00:38:10,860 --> 00:38:12,290
Do you really know me?

696
00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:14,720
If Duan Yu is the Mr Duan you mentioned,

697
00:38:14,750 --> 00:38:15,850
then I know him.

698
00:38:16,290 --> 00:38:19,350
Young Master Duan helped the Fire Crane Tribe.

699
00:38:19,410 --> 00:38:21,210
You're Young Master Duan's friend.

700
00:38:21,210 --> 00:38:23,890
Of course you're a friend of the Fire Crane Tribe.

701
00:38:23,890 --> 00:38:25,750
Duan Yu and I are not only friends,

702
00:38:26,220 --> 00:38:28,040
but also sworn friends.

703
00:38:30,120 --> 00:38:31,680
That's great.

704
00:38:31,770 --> 00:38:33,000
The Fire Crane Tribe

705
00:38:33,030 --> 00:38:35,390
will definitely treat you well.

706
00:38:35,420 --> 00:38:36,380
What a pity.

707
00:38:36,630 --> 00:38:38,380
If you really came to see Mr. Duan,

708
00:38:38,380 --> 00:38:39,670
he left ages ago.

709
00:38:40,150 --> 00:38:41,180
Where did he go?

710
00:38:41,240 --> 00:38:42,630
He went to see his fiancee.

711
00:38:42,630 --> 00:38:43,840
Fiancée?

712
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:45,980
Honored guest.

713
00:38:46,120 --> 00:38:48,230
If you want to see Young Master Duan,

714
00:38:48,270 --> 00:38:50,750
you can wait here.

715
00:38:51,070 --> 00:38:52,470
Young Master Duan said

716
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:54,100
he would come back.

717
00:38:54,140 --> 00:38:55,620
Why would Duan Yu come back?

718
00:38:55,620 --> 00:38:57,270
Because of his fiancee.

719
00:38:58,000 --> 00:38:59,390
He said his fiancee

720
00:38:59,420 --> 00:39:00,850
looks exactly like the portrait of the Goddess

721
00:39:00,850 --> 00:39:02,040
in our holy relic.

722
00:39:02,370 --> 00:39:03,160
Wu.

723
00:39:05,190 --> 00:39:07,110
It does sound a bit magical.

724
00:39:07,290 --> 00:39:10,550
May I have a chance to see it?

725
00:39:10,570 --> 00:39:13,130
The holy relic is the treasure of our clan.

726
00:39:13,330 --> 00:39:15,060
It can't be shown so easily.

727
00:39:15,080 --> 00:39:17,520
Please forgive me.

728
00:39:18,460 --> 00:39:20,220
Then how did Duan Yu see it?

729
00:39:20,250 --> 00:39:21,440
He's different.

730
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:23,610
He risked his life

731
00:39:23,700 --> 00:39:26,080
to get rid of the threat of the Moon Wolf Tribe.

732
00:39:26,080 --> 00:39:27,940
He's a true warrior.

733
00:39:28,180 --> 00:39:29,470
I see.

734
00:39:30,650 --> 00:39:32,780
Looks like I came at the right time.

735
00:39:33,570 --> 00:39:36,370
Sir, you mean...

736
00:39:41,450 --> 00:39:43,050
I'll take...

737
00:39:44,450 --> 00:39:45,450
your holy relic.
